Ford Open Prison in Arundel has the worst record for prison escapes in the country . 
  Ministry of Justice has released the names of 39 missing inmates since 2004 . 
  Among them are two murderers and drug dealers who have been missing for 10 years . 
  Robert Donovan disappeared from the prison in 2010 but it took four years to find him . 
  Derek Passmore escaped in 2013 after being jailed for beating a disabled man to death . 
 